{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1441,"text":"Speaking up is hard to do."},{"time":4588,"text":"I understood the true meaning\nof this phrase exactly one month ago,"},{"time":9531,"text":"when my wife and I became new parents."},{"time":13113,"text":"It was an amazing moment."},{"time":14815,"text":"It was exhilarating and elating,"},{"time":17024,"text":"but it was also scary and terrifying."},{"time":20369,"text":"And it got particularly terrifying\nwhen we got home from the hospital,"},{"time":24595,"text":"and we were unsure"},{"time":26080,"text":"whether our little baby boy was getting\nenough nutrients from breastfeeding."},{"time":30616,"text":"And we wanted to call our pediatrician,"},{"time":33967,"text":"but we also didn't want\nto make a bad first impression"},{"time":36566,"text":"or come across as a crazy,\nneurotic parent."},{"time":39054,"text":"So we worried."},{"time":40725,"text":"And we waited."},{"time":42131,"text":"When we got to the doctor's office\nthe next day,"},{"time":44450,"text":"she immediately gave him formula\nbecause he was pretty dehydrated."},{"time":49312,"text":"Our son is fine now,"},{"time":50770,"text":"and our doctor has reassured us\nwe can always contact her."},{"time":54106,"text":"But in that moment,"},{"time":55656,"text":"I should've spoken up, but I didn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58943,"text":"But sometimes we speak up\nwhen we shouldn't,"},{"time":62262,"text":"and I learned that over 10 years ago\nwhen I let my twin brother down."},{"time":66579,"text":"My twin brother\nis a documentary filmmaker,"},{"time":69245,"text":"and for one of his first films,"},{"time":70799,"text":"he got an offer\nfrom a distribution company."},{"time":73438,"text":"He was excited,"},{"time":74800,"text":"and he was inclined to accept the offer."},{"time":77491,"text":"But as a negotiations researcher,"},{"time":79608,"text":"I insisted he make a counteroffer,"},{"time":82585,"text":"and I helped him craft the perfect one."},{"time":85839,"text":"And it was perfect --"},{"time":87544,"text":"it was perfectly insulting."},{"time":90423,"text":"The company was so offended,"},{"time":92160,"text":"they literally withdrew the offer"},{"time":94233,"text":"and my brother was left with nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96474,"text":"And I've asked people all over the world\nabout this dilemma of speaking up:"},{"time":100358,"text":"when they can assert themselves,"},{"time":102216,"text":"when they can push their interests,"},{"time":103954,"text":"when they can express an opinion,"},{"time":106173,"text":"when they can make an ambitious ask."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108887,"text":"And the range of stories\nare varied and diverse,"},{"time":113144,"text":"but they also make up\na universal tapestry."},{"time":115839,"text":"Can I correct my boss\nwhen they make a mistake?"},{"time":118541,"text":"Can I confront my coworker\nwho keeps stepping on my toes?"},{"time":122996,"text":"Can I challenge my friend's\ninsensitive joke?"},{"time":126390,"text":"Can I tell the person I love the most\nmy deepest insecurities?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":130963,"text":"And through these experiences,\nI've come to recognize"},{"time":133700,"text":"that each of us have something called\na range of acceptable behavior."},{"time":137581,"text":"Now, sometimes we're too strong;\nwe push ourselves too much."},{"time":142856,"text":"That's what happened with my brother."},{"time":144643,"text":"Even making an offer was outside\nhis range of acceptable behavior."},{"time":149663,"text":"But sometimes we're too weak."},{"time":151211,"text":"That's what happened with my wife and I."},{"time":153299,"text":"And this range of acceptable behaviors --"},{"time":155539,"text":"when we stay within our range,\nwe're rewarded."},{"time":158658,"text":"When we step outside that range,\nwe get punished in a variety of ways."},{"time":162851,"text":"We get dismissed or demeaned\nor even ostracized."},{"time":166014,"text":"Or we lose that raise\nor that promotion or that deal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169929,"text":"Now, the first thing we need to know is:"},{"time":172717,"text":"What is my range?"},{"time":174744,"text":"But the key thing is,\nour range isn't fixed;"},{"time":179265,"text":"it's actually pretty dynamic."},{"time":180705,"text":"It expands and it narrows\nbased on the context."},{"time":185344,"text":"And there's one thing that determines\nthat range more than anything else,"},{"time":190038,"text":"and that's your power."},{"time":191355,"text":"Your power determines your range."},{"time":193536,"text":"What is power?"},{"time":194997,"text":"Power comes in lots of forms."},{"time":196788,"text":"In negotiations, it comes\nin the form of alternatives."},{"time":199901,"text":"So my brother had no alternatives;"},{"time":201925,"text":"he lacked power."},{"time":203136,"text":"The company had lots of alternatives;"},{"time":204980,"text":"they had power."},{"time":206170,"text":"Sometimes it's being new\nto a country, like an immigrant,"},{"time":209254,"text":"or new to an organization"},{"time":210737,"text":"or new to an experience,"},{"time":212320,"text":"like my wife and I as new parents."},{"time":214449,"text":"Sometimes it's at work,"},{"time":215974,"text":"where someone's the boss\nand someone's the subordinate."},{"time":218609,"text":"Sometimes it's in relationships,"},{"time":220317,"text":"where one person's more invested\nthan the other person."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223322,"text":"And the key thing is that when\nwe have lots of power,"},{"time":226861,"text":"our range is very wide."},{"time":228714,"text":"We have a lot of leeway in how to behave."},{"time":231813,"text":"But when we lack power, our range narrows."},{"time":234537,"text":"We have very little leeway."},{"time":236947,"text":"The problem is that when\nour range narrows,"},{"time":239753,"text":"that produces something called\nthe low-power double bind."},{"time":244310,"text":"The low-power double bind happens"},{"time":247007,"text":"when, if we don't speak up,\nwe go unnoticed,"},{"time":250576,"text":"but if we do speak up, we get punished."}]},{"cues":[{"time":253359,"text":"Now, many of you have heard\nthe phrase the \"double bind\""},{"time":256094,"text":"and connected it with one thing,\nand that's gender."},{"time":259065,"text":"The gender double bind is women\nwho don't speak up go unnoticed,"},{"time":263299,"text":"and women who do speak up get punished."},{"time":266127,"text":"And the key thing is that women have\nthe same need as men to speak up,"},{"time":271135,"text":"but they have barriers to doing so."},{"time":274004,"text":"But what my research has shown\nover the last two decades"},{"time":277306,"text":"is that what looks\nlike a gender difference"},{"time":281035,"text":"is not really a gender double bind,"},{"time":283456,"text":"it's a really a low-power double bind."},{"time":285836,"text":"And what looks like a gender difference"},{"time":287744,"text":"are really often just power\ndifferences in disguise."},{"time":291394,"text":"Oftentimes we see a difference\nbetween a man and a woman"},{"time":294141,"text":"or men and women,"},{"time":295363,"text":"and think, \"Biological cause.\nThere's something fundamentally different"},{"time":298995,"text":"about the sexes.\""},{"time":300265,"text":"But in study after study,"},{"time":302143,"text":"I've found that a better explanation\nfor many sex differences"},{"time":306893,"text":"is really power."},{"time":308429,"text":"And so it's the low-power double bind."},{"time":311975,"text":"And the low-power double bind\nmeans that we have a narrow range,"},{"time":316815,"text":"and we lack power."},{"time":318669,"text":"We have a narrow range,"},{"time":319925,"text":"and our double bind is very large."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322335,"text":"So we need to find ways\nto expand our range."},{"time":324715,"text":"And over the last couple decades,"},{"time":326316,"text":"my colleagues and I have found\ntwo things really matter."},{"time":329887,"text":"The first: you seem powerful\nin your own eyes."},{"time":334284,"text":"The second: you seem powerful\nin the eyes of others."},{"time":337629,"text":"When I feel powerful,"},{"time":340117,"text":"I feel confident, not fearful;"},{"time":342016,"text":"I expand my own range."},{"time":343882,"text":"When other people see me as powerful,"},{"time":346614,"text":"they grant me a wider range."},{"time":349174,"text":"So we need tools to expand\nour range of acceptable behavior."},{"time":353952,"text":"And I'm going to give you\na set of tools today."},{"time":356367,"text":"Speaking up is risky,"},{"time":358503,"text":"but these tools will lower\nyour risk of speaking up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363067,"text":"The first tool I'm going to give you\ngot discovered in negotiations"},{"time":368925,"text":"in an important finding."},{"time":370329,"text":"On average, women make\nless ambitious offers"},{"time":374249,"text":"and get worse outcomes than men\nat the bargaining table."},{"time":378200,"text":"But Hannah Riley Bowles\nand Emily Amanatullah have discovered"},{"time":381341,"text":"there's one situation\nwhere women get the same outcomes as men"},{"time":385043,"text":"and are just as ambitious."},{"time":387196,"text":"That's when they advocate for others."},{"time":391251,"text":"When they advocate for others,"},{"time":393412,"text":"they discover their own range\nand expand it in their own mind."},{"time":398313,"text":"They become more assertive."},{"time":399746,"text":"This is sometimes called\n\"the mama bear effect.\""},{"time":403483,"text":"Like a mama bear defending her cubs,"},{"time":405766,"text":"when we advocate for others,\nwe can discover our own voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410328,"text":"But sometimes, we have\nto advocate for ourselves."},{"time":413469,"text":"How do we do that?"},{"time":414833,"text":"One of the most important tools\nwe have to advocate for ourselves"},{"time":418862,"text":"is something called perspective-taking."},{"time":421258,"text":"And perspective-taking is really simple:"},{"time":424034,"text":"it's simply looking at the world\nthrough the eyes of another person."},{"time":429014,"text":"It's one of the most important tools\nwe have to expand our range."},{"time":432826,"text":"When I take your perspective,"},{"time":434557,"text":"and I think about what you really want,"},{"time":437020,"text":"you're more likely to give me\nwhat I really want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":441461,"text":"But here's the problem:"},{"time":442985,"text":"perspective-taking is hard to do."},{"time":445290,"text":"So let's do a little experiment."},{"time":446844,"text":"I want you all to hold\nyour hand just like this:"},{"time":449882,"text":"your finger -- put it up."},{"time":451770,"text":"And I want you to draw\na capital letter E on your forehead"},{"time":456026,"text":"as quickly as possible."},{"time":460066,"text":"OK, it turns out that we can\ndraw this E in one of two ways,"},{"time":463407,"text":"and this was originally designed\nas a test of perspective-taking."},{"time":466916,"text":"I'm going to show you two pictures"},{"time":468861,"text":"of someone with an E on their forehead --"},{"time":470885,"text":"my former student, Erika Hall."},{"time":473294,"text":"And you can see over here,"},{"time":475286,"text":"that's the correct E."},{"time":476577,"text":"I drew the E so it looks like\nan E to another person."},{"time":480051,"text":"That's the perspective-taking E"},{"time":482182,"text":"because it looks like an E\nfrom someone else's vantage point."},{"time":485261,"text":"But this E over here\nis the self-focused E."},{"time":488856,"text":"We often get self-focused."},{"time":490533,"text":"And we particularly get\nself-focused in a crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494064,"text":"I want to tell you\nabout a particular crisis."},{"time":496259,"text":"A man walks into a bank\nin Watsonville, California."},{"time":500285,"text":"And he says, \"Give me $2,000,"},{"time":502748,"text":"or I'm blowing the whole bank\nup with a bomb.\""},{"time":505503,"text":"Now, the bank manager\ndidn't give him the money."},{"time":508052,"text":"She took a step back."},{"time":509873,"text":"She took his perspective,"},{"time":511353,"text":"and she noticed something\nreally important."},{"time":513744,"text":"He asked for a specific amount of money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":516474,"text":"So she said,"},{"time":518669,"text":"\"Why did you ask for $2,000?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":521265,"text":"And he said, \"My friend\nis going to be evicted"},{"time":523657,"text":"unless I get him $2,000 immediately.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":525944,"text":"And she said, \"Oh! You don't want\nto rob the bank --"},{"time":529018,"text":"you want to take out a loan.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":530530,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":531639,"text":"\"Why don't you come back to my office,"},{"time":533536,"text":"and we can have you\nfill out the paperwork.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":535739,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":537214,"text":"Now, her quick perspective-taking\ndefused a volatile situation."},{"time":542276,"text":"So when we take someone's perspective,"},{"time":544119,"text":"it allows us to be ambitious\nand assertive, but still be likable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549182,"text":"Here's another way to be assertive\nbut still be likable,"},{"time":552474,"text":"and that is to signal flexibility."},{"time":555413,"text":"Now, imagine you're a car salesperson,\nand you want to sell someone a car."},{"time":559790,"text":"You're going to more likely make the sale\nif you give them two options."},{"time":564141,"text":"Let's say option A:"},{"time":565588,"text":"$24,000 for this car\nand a five-year warranty."},{"time":569084,"text":"Or option B:"},{"time":570701,"text":"$23,000 and a three-year warranty."},{"time":573845,"text":"My research shows that when you give\npeople a choice among options,"},{"time":577447,"text":"it lowers their defenses,"},{"time":579360,"text":"and they're more likely\nto accept your offer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582202,"text":"And this doesn't just\nwork with salespeople;"},{"time":584343,"text":"it works with parents."},{"time":585558,"text":"When my niece was four,"},{"time":586861,"text":"she resisted getting dressed\nand rejected everything."},{"time":590160,"text":"But then my sister-in-law\nhad a brilliant idea."},{"time":593079,"text":"What if I gave my daughter a choice?"},{"time":595654,"text":"This shirt or that shirt? OK, that shirt."},{"time":597699,"text":"This pant or that pant? OK, that pant."},{"time":599845,"text":"And it worked brilliantly."},{"time":601207,"text":"She got dressed quickly\nand without resistance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605498,"text":"When I've asked the question\naround the world"},{"time":607809,"text":"when people feel comfortable speaking up,"},{"time":609884,"text":"the number one answer is:"},{"time":611244,"text":"\"When I have social support\nin my audience; when I have allies.\""},{"time":616022,"text":"So we want to get allies on our side."},{"time":619957,"text":"How do we do that?"},{"time":621841,"text":"Well, one of the ways is be a mama bear."},{"time":624034,"text":"When we advocate for others,"},{"time":625534,"text":"we expand our range in our own eyes\nand the eyes of others,"},{"time":629087,"text":"but we also earn strong allies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631806,"text":"Another way we can earn strong allies,\nespecially in high places,"},{"time":636537,"text":"is by asking other people for advice."},{"time":639410,"text":"When we ask others for advice,\nthey like us because we flatter them,"},{"time":645315,"text":"and we're expressing humility."},{"time":647281,"text":"And this really works to solve\nanother double bind."},{"time":650831,"text":"And that's the self-promotion double bind."},{"time":653498,"text":"The self-promotion double bind"},{"time":655026,"text":"is that if we don't advertise\nour accomplishments,"},{"time":658205,"text":"no one notices."},{"time":659439,"text":"And if we do, we're not likable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661867,"text":"But if we ask for advice\nabout one of our accomplishments,"},{"time":665457,"text":"we are able to be competent\nin their eyes but also be likeable."},{"time":670495,"text":"And this is so powerful"},{"time":672526,"text":"it even works when you see it coming."},{"time":675469,"text":"There have been multiple times in life\nwhen I have been forewarned"},{"time":679533,"text":"that a low-power person has been given\nthe advice to come ask me for advice."},{"time":684289,"text":"I want you to notice\nthree things about this:"},{"time":686555,"text":"First, I knew they were going\nto come ask me for advice."},{"time":689930,"text":"Two, I've actually done research\non the strategic benefits"},{"time":693956,"text":"of asking for advice."},{"time":695882,"text":"And three, it still worked!"},{"time":698656,"text":"I took their perspective,"},{"time":699897,"text":"I became more invested in their cause,"},{"time":702108,"text":"I became more committed to them\nbecause they asked for advice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706343,"text":"Now, another time we feel\nmore confident speaking up"},{"time":709949,"text":"is when we have expertise."},{"time":712144,"text":"Expertise gives us credibility."},{"time":714862,"text":"When we have high power,\nwe already have credibility."},{"time":717813,"text":"We only need good evidence."},{"time":719777,"text":"When we lack power,\nwe don't have the credibility."},{"time":722771,"text":"We need excellent evidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725394,"text":"And one of the ways\nwe can come across as an expert"},{"time":729165,"text":"is by tapping into our passion."},{"time":731784,"text":"I want everyone in the next few days\nto go up to friend of theirs"},{"time":735982,"text":"and just say to them,"},{"time":737251,"text":"\"I want you to describe\na passion of yours to me.\""},{"time":740738,"text":"I've had people do this all over the world"},{"time":743247,"text":"and I asked them,"},{"time":744527,"text":"\"What did you notice\nabout the other person"},{"time":746720,"text":"when they described their passion?\""},{"time":748798,"text":"And the answers are always the same."},{"time":750722,"text":"\"Their eyes lit up and got big.\""},{"time":752754,"text":"\"They smiled a big beaming smile.\""},{"time":755727,"text":"\"They used their hands all over --"},{"time":757395,"text":"I had to duck because their\nhands were coming at me.\""},{"time":759911,"text":"\"They talk quickly\nwith a little higher pitch.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":762136,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":763134,"text":"\"They leaned in\nas if telling me a secret.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":765602,"text":"And then I said to them,"},{"time":766947,"text":"\"What happened to you\nas you listened to their passion?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":770374,"text":"They said, \"My eyes lit up."},{"time":772678,"text":"I smiled."},{"time":773972,"text":"I leaned in.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":775369,"text":"When we tap into our passion,"},{"time":777462,"text":"we give ourselves the courage,\nin our own eyes, to speak up,"},{"time":780852,"text":"but we also get the permission\nfrom others to speak up."},{"time":784534,"text":"Tapping into our passion even works\nwhen we come across as too weak."},{"time":790533,"text":"Both men and women get punished\nat work when they shed tears."},{"time":795344,"text":"But Lizzie Wolf has shown that when\nwe frame our strong emotions as passion,"},{"time":801786,"text":"the condemnation of our crying\ndisappears for both men and women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":808598,"text":"I want to end with a few words\nfrom my late father"},{"time":812090,"text":"that he spoke at my twin\nbrother's wedding."},{"time":814675,"text":"Here's a picture of us."},{"time":817664,"text":"My dad was a psychologist like me,"},{"time":819945,"text":"but his real love and his real\npassion was cinema,"},{"time":823691,"text":"like my brother."},{"time":824915,"text":"And so he wrote a speech\nfor my brother's wedding"},{"time":827505,"text":"about the roles we play\nin the human comedy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":830678,"text":"And he said, \"The lighter your touch,"},{"time":832991,"text":"the better you become at improving\nand enriching your performance."},{"time":837170,"text":"Those who embrace their roles\nand work to improve their performance"},{"time":842001,"text":"grow, change and expand the self."},{"time":845067,"text":"Play it well,"},{"time":846399,"text":"and your days will be mostly joyful.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":848946,"text":"What my dad was saying"},{"time":850595,"text":"is that we've all been assigned\nranges and roles in this world."},{"time":855048,"text":"But he was also saying\nthe essence of this talk:"},{"time":859005,"text":"those roles and ranges are constantly\nexpanding and evolving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":864770,"text":"So when a scene calls for it,"},{"time":867114,"text":"be a ferocious mama bear"},{"time":869251,"text":"and a humble advice seeker."},{"time":871802,"text":"Have excellent evidence and strong allies."},{"time":875910,"text":"Be a passionate perspective taker."},{"time":878770,"text":"And if you use those tools --"},{"time":880514,"text":"and each and every one of you\ncan use these tools --"},{"time":884104,"text":"you will expand your range\nof acceptable behavior,"},{"time":887994,"text":"and your days will be mostly joyful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":892082,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":893256,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}